rows.label: qst400909_msg0002
rows.name:
So the suspicious facility
is near the chest of the
Superbian Divine Beast?

rows.label: qst400909_msg0003
rows.name:
Yes. After watching for a while,
it seems a Nopon came and
transported the materials there.

rows.label: qst400909_msg0004
rows.name:
For now, we must report
to the Flamebringer.

rows.label: qst400909_msg0006
rows.name:
If we go to the palace and
tell the guards, they'll
arrange a meeting, right?

rows.label: qst400909_msg0008
rows.name:
I hope we don't get surrounded
and have to fight again.
